<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉的父亲出去打猎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，继母叫醒了艾拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“起来，你这个懒丫头。”她厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有件事儿告诉你。你父亲死了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼中充满了泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！”她痛哭起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸！我可怜的父亲......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那之后，一切都变了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉仍然又善良，又有礼貌，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但继母现在却很坏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>继母把漂亮的衣服给了自己的女儿们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉却穿着又丑又旧的衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>继姐姐们睡在柔软舒适的床上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉却睡在一张用稻草做的硬床上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格特整天睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特鲁迪整天吃个不停。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉却得每天干活儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她擦洗、清扫、拖地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“漂亮的小艾拉。”继母说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你以为你比我们强。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你也以为你更漂亮。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我没有！”艾拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您和姐姐们，现在是我的家人了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我爱你们大家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哼。”继母冷笑道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你很善良啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>去给我做午饭吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>再去看看火炉！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不想让我的女儿们感冒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉喜欢坐在火炉旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她记得和父亲在一起的日子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好想爸爸。”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>继姐姐们看见艾拉坐在火炉边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特鲁迪咯咯地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你满身都是灰尘！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“艾拉喜欢灰尘和煤渣。”格特说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们叫艾拉灰姑娘吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>